  Name: Wild Leap
  Description: Berserker leaps towards the selected enemy. All movement restricting
    effects are removed, and Berserker is immune to them for 3 seconds. Inflicts
    $X damage to the target and surrounding enemies. If no target is selected, Berserker
    will leap a distance of up to 24 yards. If stunned, feared, disoriented or immobilized,
    Berserker can break free once every 20 seconds by using Wild Leap.
